<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>帛琉五天四夜潛旅行程 2026</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ocean-deep: #0a3d5c;
    --ocean-mid: #0e6b8f;
    --ocean-bright: #1a9cbf;
    --ocean-light: #4dc8e8;
    --teal: #0d9488;
    --teal-light: #5eead4;
    --sand: #fdf6e3;
    --sand-dark: #f5e6c8;
    --coral: #f97316;
    --coral-light: #fed7aa;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --text-dark: #0f2d3d;
    --text-mid: #2d6a87;
    --text-light: #64a6c0;
    --green-dive: #065f46;
    --green-light: #d1fae5;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
    background: var(--sand);
    color: var(--text-dark);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--ocean-deep) 0%, var(--ocean-mid) 50%, var(--ocean-bright) 100%);
    padding: 80px 24px 100px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2px; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 60px;
    background: var(--sand);
    clip-path: ellipse(55% 100% at 50% 100%);
  }

  .hero-wave {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    opacity: 0.06;
    background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(
      -45deg,
      transparent,
      transparent 20px,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 20px,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 22px
    );
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    color: var(--teal-light);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    padding: 6px 18px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .hero-chip {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    color: white;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  /* CONTAINER */
  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  /* SECTION TITLE */
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--ocean-deep);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .section-title::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--ocean-light), transparent);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  /* DAY CARDS */
  .days-section {
    padding: 60px 0 40px;
  }

  .day-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(10,61,92,0.08);
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .day-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
  .day-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
  .day-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
  .day-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.35s; }
  .day-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.45s; }

  .day-header {
    padding: 20px 28px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .day-header.blue { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean-deep), var(--ocean-mid)); }
  .day-header.teal { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #065f46, var(--teal)); }
  .day-header.coral { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #92400e, var(--coral)); }

  .day-num {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .day-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .day-date {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .day-icon {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .day-body {
    padding: 24px 28px;
  }

  /* SCHEDULE TABLE */
  .schedule {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .schedule tr {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f4f8;
  }

  .schedule tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .schedule td {
    padding: 10px 8px;
    vertical-align: top;
  }

  .schedule td:first-child {
    color: var(--ocean-bright);
    font-weight: 700;
    white-space: nowrap;
    width: 70px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .schedule td:last-child {
    color: var(--text-dark);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .tag-included {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--green-light);
    color: var(--green-dive);
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-left: 6px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* DIVE SPOTS */
  .dive-spots {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f7fa, #e8f5e9);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .dive-spots-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--teal);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .dive-spot-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .dive-spot-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .spot-name {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ocean-deep);
    min-width: 160px;
  }

  .spot-detail {
    color: #4a7080;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* SNORKEL SPOTS */
  .snorkel-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .snorkel-item {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff8e1, #fff3cd);
    border: 1px solid #fde68a;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .snorkel-emoji { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }

  .snorkel-name {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #92400e;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .snorkel-desc {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #b45309;
  }

  /* NOTICES */
  .notices {
    background: #fff8f0;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--coral);
    border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .notices-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--coral);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .notices ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .notices ul li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #7c3a1a;
    padding: 3px 0;
    padding-left: 16px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .notices ul li::before {
    content: '▸';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--coral);
    font-size: 11px;
    top: 4px;
  }

  /* FLIGHT INFO */
  .flight-bar {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f2fe, #bae6fd);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .flight-code {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ocean-deep);
  }

  .flight-route {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .flight-arrow {
    color: var(--ocean-bright);
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .flight-time {
    margin-left: auto;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .flight-time strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ocean-deep);
  }

  .flight-time span {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  /* HOTEL SECTION */
  .hotel-section {
    padding: 20px 0 40px;
  }

  .hotel-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(10,61,92,0.08);
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hotel-banner {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean-deep), var(--teal));
    padding: 32px 28px;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 220px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hotel-banner h3 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .hotel-banner p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .hotel-link {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    color: white;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .hotel-link:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); }

  .hotel-details {
    padding: 28px;
    flex: 2;
    min-width: 260px;
  }

  .hotel-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f4f8;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .hotel-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .hotel-row span:first-child { color: var(--text-light); }
  .hotel-row span:last-child { font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-dark); }

  /* COST SECTION */
  .cost-section {
    padding: 20px 0 40px;
  }

  .cost-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cost-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(10,61,92,0.07);
  }

  .cost-card-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid;
  }

  .cost-card.prepaid .cost-card-title {
    color: var(--teal);
    border-color: var(--teal-light);
  }

  .cost-card.onsite .cost-card-title {
    color: var(--ocean-mid);
    border-color: var(--ocean-light);
  }

  .cost-card.extra .cost-card-title {
    color: #92400e;
    border-color: #fde68a;
  }

  .cost-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 8px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f8fa;
  }

  .cost-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .cost-label { color: #4a6070; }
  .cost-sub { font-size: 11px; color: #8aa0b0; display: block; margin-top: 2px; }

  .cost-amount {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .cost-card.prepaid .cost-amount { color: var(--teal); }
  .cost-card.onsite .cost-amount { color: var(--ocean-mid); }
  .cost-card.extra .cost-amount { color: #92400e; }

  .cost-total {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean-deep), var(--ocean-mid));
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 20px 28px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .cost-total-label {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .cost-total-amount {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .cost-total-sub {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }

  /* BANK */
  .bank-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(10,61,92,0.07);
    margin-top: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .bank-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22d3ee, #06b6d4);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .bank-info h4 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ocean-deep);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .bank-info p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .bank-amount {
    margin-left: auto;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .bank-amount strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ocean-deep);
  }

  .bank-amount span {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  /* TIPS SECTION */
  .tips-section {
    padding: 20px 0 60px;
  }

  .tips-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .tip-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(10,61,92,0.07);
  }

  .tip-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .tip-emoji {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .tip-emoji.blue { background: #e0f2fe; }
  .tip-emoji.teal { background: #d1fae5; }
  .tip-emoji.yellow { background: #fef3c7; }
  .tip-emoji.orange { background: #fff7ed; }
  .tip-emoji.green { background: #ecfdf5; }
  .tip-emoji.pink { background: #fdf2f8; }

  .tip-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ocean-deep);
  }

  .tip-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .tip-card ul li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #4a6070;
    padding: 4px 0;
    padding-left: 14px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f8fa;
  }

  .tip-card ul li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .tip-card ul li::before {
    content: '·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 4px;
    color: var(--ocean-bright);
    font-size: 16px;
    top: 1px;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--ocean-deep);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 32px 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  footer strong { color: white; }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .wave-divider {
    height: 40px;
    background: white;
    clip-path: ellipse(55% 100% at 50% 0%);
    margin-bottom: -2px;
  }

  .section-bg-white { background: white; }
  .section-bg-sand { background: var(--sand); }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .day-header { padding: 16px 18px; }
    .day-body { padding: 18px; }
    .dive-spot-item { flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
    .spot-name { min-width: unset; }
    .hotel-card { flex-direction: column; }
    .cost-total { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    .bank-card { flex-direction: column; }
    .bank-amount { margin-left: 0; text-align: left; }
    .schedule td:first-child { width: 60px; font-size: 12px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-wave"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-badge">🌊 2026 潛旅行程</div>
    <h1>帛琉五天四夜<br>潛旅之旅</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">LT Dive Palau × Thalassa × IPRC Palau</p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="hero-chip">📅 6月18日 ─ 6月22日</div>
      <div class="hero-chip">🛫 CI30 / CI29 中華航空</div>
      <div class="hero-chip">🏨 IPRC Palau 4晚</div>
      <div class="hero-chip">🤿 AOW 考照</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- DAY CARDS -->
<div class="section-bg-sand">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="days-section">
      <h2 class="section-title">📋 每日行程</h2>

      <!-- DAY 1 -->
      <div class="day-card">
        <div class="day-header blue">
          <div>
            <div class="day-num">Day 1</div>
            <div class="day-title">抵達帛琉</div>
            <div class="day-date">6月18日（四）</div>
          </div>
          <div class="day-icon">✈️</div>
        </div>
        <div class="day-body">
          <div class="flight-bar">
            <div class="flight-code">CI30</div>
            <div class="flight-route">
              <span>桃園 T1</span>
              <span class="flight-arrow">→</span>
              <span>帛琉 ROR</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flight-time">
              <strong>09:40 → 14:35</strong>
              <span>中華航空 A321 NEO</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <table class="schedule">
            <tr><td>14:35</td><td>抵達帛琉機場（ROR）</td></tr>
            <tr><td>15:00</td><td>LT Dive 機場接送至飯店（車程約30分鐘）</td></tr>
            <tr><td>15:30</td><td>IPRC Palau Check-in</td></tr>
            <tr><td>16:00</td><td>休息、整理裝備、填寫 LT Dive 資料表</td></tr>
            <tr><td>19:00</td><td>晚餐（自理）</td></tr>
          </table>
          <div class="notices">
            <div class="notices-title">⚠️ 注意事項</div>
            <ul>
              <li>入境前72小時需至 palautravel.pw 填寫入境表格，取得入境 QR Code</li>
              <li>入境時須提供入境 QR Code + 回程機票憑證（電子版即可）</li>
              <li>機場內無找換店，請事先備好美金現金</li>
              <li>入境限帶：19支香煙、2公升酒精</li>
              <li>時區較台灣快1小時（UTC+9）</li>
              <li>抵達後建議盡快購買當地 SIM 卡（PNCC 或 PT WAVE）</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- DAY 2 -->
      <div class="day-card">
        <div class="day-header teal">
          <div>
            <div class="day-num">Day 2</div>
            <div class="day-title">AOW 課程 Day 1</div>
            <div class="day-date">6月19日（五）｜LT Dive Palau</div>
          </div>
          <div class="day-icon">🤿</div>
        </div>
        <div class="day-body">
          <table class="schedule">
            <tr><td>07:00</td><td>飯店早餐 <span class="tag-included">含</span>（不要吃太飽）</td></tr>
            <tr><td>08:30</td><td>LT Dive 接駁上船</td></tr>
            <tr><td>09:30</td><td>第一潛：藍洞 Blue Holes（深潛科目）</td></tr>
            <tr><td>11:15</td><td>第二潛：大斷層 Big Drop-off（多層次電腦錶科目）</td></tr>
            <tr><td>12:00</td><td>午餐 <span class="tag-included">含</span></td></tr>
            <tr><td>14:00</td><td>第三潛：玻璃城 Glass City（導航科目）</td></tr>
            <tr><td>15:00</td><td>回程，飯店梳洗休息</td></tr>
            <tr><td>19:00</td><td>晚餐（自理）</td></tr>
          </table>
          <div class="dive-spots">
            <div class="dive-spots-title">🐟 潛點介紹</div>
            <div class="dive-spot-item">
              <div class="spot-name">🔵 藍洞 Blue Holes</div>
              <div class="spot-detail">流況弱｜最大深度 30M｜天使曙光、心型洞、閃電貝</div>
            </div>
            <div class="dive-spot-item">
              <div class="spot-name">🪸 大斷層 Big Drop-off</div>
              <div class="spot-detail">流況弱至中｜最大深度 20M｜巨型海扇、七彩珊瑚、玳瑁海龜</div>
            </div>
            <div class="dive-spot-item">
              <div class="spot-name">🐟 玻璃城 Glass City</div>
              <div class="spot-detail">流況弱至中｜最大深度 30M｜魟魚清潔站、杰克魚群</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="notices">
            <div class="notices-title">⚠️ 注意事項</div>
            <ul>
              <li>請攜帶：電腦錶、浮力袋（SMB）、手電筒</li>
              <li>禁止攜帶手套（帛琉政府規定）</li>
              <li>潛水前8小時勿飲酒</li>
              <li>使用珊瑚友善／物理性防曬，違規罰款 $1,000 USD</li>
              <li>暈船藥（小白兔）當天早上提早服用，早餐不要吃太飽</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
